imdb.plot outline: An adaptation of "Don Quijote and Sancho Panza" of Miguel de Cervantes, this mini series tells the story of Willy and Sandro who run a car repair shop in the town of Garzon, Uruguay. One day they are brought a car for repairs but Willy discovers that it is a car he used to own and ride around with his teenage girlfriend. So instead of repairing it they still, and go to find Angelica in Montevideo, the capital of Uruguay.
